<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Site Visit Invitation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
        }
        .container {
            width: 80%;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .header {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .content {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .content p {
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .links a {
            color: #1E90FF;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-style: italic;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <p class="header">Dear {!Lead.Salutation} {!Lead.FirstName} {!Lead.LastName},</p>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p>We are delighted to invite you to visit our site at Epitome Integrated City. Your scheduled visit is set for <strong>{!Lead.Schedule_Date_Time__c}</strong>. Our team is excited to show you around and provide a comprehensive overview of our project.</p>

            <p>Please feel free to reach out to us if you have any questions or need further assistance before the visit.</p>

            <p><strong>Location:</strong> <a href="{!Lead.Site_Location__c}" class="links">View on Google Maps</a></p>
        </div>

        <p class="footer">Warm Regards, <br> Epitome Projects LLP</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>